item.title: [PROBLEM] Gzip ProBlem Please Help? [HELP]
item.dc:creator: @badger41 badger41
item.description:
@badger41 wrote:

gzip isnt a runnable program, you have to open a .dat file with it and it auto gzip’s it for you.
right click on the .dat file and choose ‘open with’ and wherever gzip is located, open it with the gzip.exe.

for easier gzipping in the future, i would choose the ‘always use this program for opening this type of file’
thats not exactly it, but its similar and you should be able to recognize what i mean.
